1
00:00:25,079 --> 00:00:25,519
Hey!

2
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:27,440
Are you a ghost?

3
00:00:27,440 --> 00:00:28,519
You walk without a sound.

4
00:00:29,559 --> 00:00:31,920
No wonder, you're pounding herbs so loud.

5
00:00:33,759 --> 00:00:36,359
Ren Feifan, act like a decent human.

6
00:00:37,039 --> 00:00:37,880
All these years you were gone,

7
00:00:37,880 --> 00:00:39,719
I was the one caring for her and her mom.

8
00:00:41,359 --> 00:00:41,880
Fine.

9
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:45,079
Miss Jiang, please accept my humble bow.

10
00:00:46,679 --> 00:00:47,320
Oh, cut it out.

11
00:00:48,479 --> 00:00:50,039
With that silver tongue of yours,

12
00:00:50,039 --> 00:00:52,880
you could coax sparrows from the trees.

13
00:00:55,719 --> 00:00:56,920
Did you come just to mock me?

14
00:00:57,600 --> 00:00:58,799
Spit it out. What is it?

15
00:01:01,320 --> 00:01:01,880
Ren Feifan,

16
00:01:03,000 --> 00:01:04,480
don't you think

17
00:01:04,640 --> 00:01:07,400
Ruo Jin is a bit different than before?

18
00:01:11,719 --> 00:01:13,040
She is a bit different.

19
00:01:15,319 --> 00:01:16,079
She's become

20
00:01:17,239 --> 00:01:18,599
much more resilient than before.

21
00:01:19,879 --> 00:01:20,760
That's a good thing.

22
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,000
What?

23
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,640
Do you think something's wrong with...

24
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:30,640
Where'd he go?

25
00:01:31,599 --> 00:01:33,040
Vanished again.

26
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:58,560
Feifan, time to wake up!

27
00:02:09,360 --> 00:02:10,719
You slept so soundly.

28
00:02:21,199 --> 00:02:21,759
You're awake.

29
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:24,120
I... I was just...

30
00:02:26,560 --> 00:02:27,680
How did you sleep last night?

31
00:02:28,919 --> 00:02:29,719
Pretty well.

32
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:30,719
What about you?

33
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:32,479
Is your cold any better?

34
00:02:33,560 --> 00:02:35,560
I still don't feel that great.

35
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:36,960
Then let me go prepare your medicine.

36
00:02:37,319 --> 00:02:37,680
No need.

37
00:02:38,599 --> 00:02:40,240
I've got some here. I already bought it.

38
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:40,960
Let me prepare it for you.

39
00:03:01,439 --> 00:03:01,800
Hold on.

40
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,400
What's wrong?

41
00:03:06,199 --> 00:03:07,520
Is something wrong with this medicine?

42
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:10,120
The smell of Aconite.

43
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,759
It's the same as that prescription.

44
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:14,639
Where did you buy this?

45
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,680
From the pharmacy nearby.

46
00:03:51,360 --> 00:03:52,199
What are you doing here?

47
00:03:52,599 --> 00:03:53,960
Weren't you watching Premier Medical Hall?

48
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:54,840
What am I doing here?

49
00:03:54,840 --> 00:03:55,840
You never call me when there's a fight.

50
00:03:56,159 --> 00:03:57,280
I came all the way back from abroad,

51
00:03:57,280 --> 00:03:58,240
not to babysit your place.

52
00:03:58,599 --> 00:03:59,599
Then what do you want?

53
00:04:00,719 --> 00:04:01,719
Do you know for four years abroad,

54
00:04:01,719 --> 00:04:03,199
I trained in European-style Taekwondo?

55
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:04,719
So?

56
00:04:05,479 --> 00:04:05,800
So...

57
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:09,639
Watch this!

58
00:04:18,480 --> 00:04:19,120
Nobody move!

59
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,040
Behave yourselves!

60
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:21,439
Don't move!

61
00:04:31,959 --> 00:04:33,399
Alright, we've got the evidence.

62
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:35,319
Time to go see Wang Chengren.

63
00:04:35,639 --> 00:04:37,639
Time to take down the big boss.

64
00:04:37,879 --> 00:04:38,160
Right.

65
00:04:38,920 --> 00:04:40,160
I, Young Master Gu, can handle it alone.

66
00:04:40,360 --> 00:04:42,040
How could you handle it alone?

67
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:44,959
Hello?

68
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:48,360
A huge crowd just showed up.

69
00:04:49,839 --> 00:04:50,279
Alright.

70
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,920
I'll head back right now.

71
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:57,480
Young Master Gu,

72
00:04:57,959 --> 00:04:59,319
we'll do it your way then.

73
00:04:59,879 --> 00:05:01,079
Go see Wang Chengren yourself.

74
00:05:02,439 --> 00:05:03,000
Remember,

75
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:04,720
just hand him over to the police.

76
00:05:05,000 --> 00:05:06,319
Don't complicate things.

77
00:05:08,800 --> 00:05:09,879
You're not joking with me, are you?

78
00:05:09,879 --> 00:05:10,480
No, I'm not.

79
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,360
This is our final showdown.

80
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,439
You're not gonna finish it with me?

81
00:05:14,439 --> 00:05:16,079
A crowd swarmed Premier Medical Hall.

82
00:05:16,079 --> 00:05:17,079
They can't handle it.

83
00:05:17,519 --> 00:05:18,800
I have to rush back right away.

84
00:05:19,319 --> 00:05:21,040
Besides, compared to fighting,

85
00:05:21,519 --> 00:05:22,480
I prefer saving lives.

86
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:26,480
What's wrong?

87
00:05:27,879 --> 00:05:28,959
Young Master Gu, are you scared?

88
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:31,920
Scared?

89
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:36,279
I, Young Master Gu, fear no one.

90
00:05:36,439 --> 00:05:38,959
I love things like punishing the wicked.

91
00:05:53,439 --> 00:05:54,000
You old bastard!

92
00:05:54,959 --> 00:05:55,600
Trying to run?

93
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:56,839
What are you gonna do?

94
00:05:57,759 --> 00:05:58,399
What am I gonna do?

95
00:05:59,600 --> 00:06:00,319
Eliminate a public menace, of course.

96
00:06:00,319 --> 00:06:01,439
I've come to finish you off!

97
00:06:02,720 --> 00:06:04,639
Wang Chengren, you're one sick freak.

98
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:07,319
Dragging the whole city down with you.

99
00:06:08,360 --> 00:06:09,279
You're an animal.

100
00:06:16,639 --> 00:06:17,000
Don't...

101
00:06:17,639 --> 00:06:18,120
Stay away from me!

102
00:06:20,959 --> 00:06:21,639
Animal?

103
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:22,920
I'm the animal?

104
00:06:23,319 --> 00:06:24,279
They're the animals.

105
00:06:25,279 --> 00:06:26,680
What do those people have?

106
00:06:26,959 --> 00:06:27,959
Nothing at all.

107
00:06:28,399 --> 00:06:30,879
Can't even afford three meals a day.

108
00:06:31,240 --> 00:06:34,240
People living like ants,

109
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:36,120
what's the difference if they live or die?

110
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:39,920
My life is worth a thousand times theirs.

111
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:43,240
They trade their lives for money.

112
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:45,120
They're all test subjects for my drugs.

113
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:51,879
Your drugs?

114
00:06:53,759 --> 00:06:55,399
So you don't make drugs to save people,

115
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:57,439
but to save your own life.

116
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,120
I...

117
00:06:59,639 --> 00:07:01,160
Is saving myself a crime?

118
00:07:01,560 --> 00:07:05,600
One dies, the family gets rich. Good deal?

119
00:07:15,360 --> 00:07:16,920
Still trying to fight me, you old fossil?

120
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:17,759
The pills!

121
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,120
My pills!

122
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,279
I was wrong to insult you.

123
00:07:24,639 --> 00:07:25,439
I insulted the animals.

124
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,759
Animals are way better than you.

125
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:38,759
I can't die!

126
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:40,759
I can't die!

127
00:07:41,279 --> 00:07:42,560
I still have so much money!

128
00:09:02,039 --> 00:09:02,720
What are you doing here?

129
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:06,759
If you can't say anything nice, shut up.

130
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:11,279
Ruo Jin said you wanted our ER records.

131
00:09:11,879 --> 00:09:12,159
Yeah.

132
00:09:13,200 --> 00:09:13,960
I brought them for you.

133
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,600
You brought them?

134
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:16,679
Yeah.

135
00:09:22,559 --> 00:09:23,799
Did you organize all these yourself?

136
00:09:25,120 --> 00:09:28,039
Obviously. We psychiatrists

137
00:09:28,039 --> 00:09:29,080
also had to finish every

138
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:31,320
basic course in med school, okay?

139
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,120
Alright, alright, fine.

140
00:09:34,480 --> 00:09:36,720
What, are they no help?

141
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:40,120
I need to study them first to know that.

142
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,440
Which herb are you still missing?

143
00:09:48,320 --> 00:09:49,519
How about I take a look for you?

144
00:09:49,960 --> 00:09:52,600
Western medicine might offer a new angle.

145
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:56,519
What are you doing?

146
00:09:56,519 --> 00:09:59,000
My beauty-enhancing pomegranate juice.

147
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,279
Men can't drink it!

148
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,360
I didn't drink it.

149
00:10:01,919 --> 00:10:03,039
You'd better not.

150
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:05,080
Did you add Herbal extract to it?

151
00:10:06,159 --> 00:10:06,720
Yeah.

152
00:10:07,519 --> 00:10:10,360
That's no big deal in Western medicine.

153
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,159
Why didn't I think of that?

154
00:10:12,679 --> 00:10:14,440
Isn't Chinese patent medicine made so?

155
00:10:17,879 --> 00:10:19,080
It's a piece of cake.

156
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:20,120
Glad I could help.

